com.epoch.chem

Class WavyBondMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • chemaxon.sss.search.MolComparator
      • com.epoch.chem.WavyBondMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StereoConstants

    public final class WavyBondMatcher
extends MolComparator
implements StereoConstants
    Alters normal JChem matching behavior so that a query wavy bond matches only to a target wavy bond, but a query single bond continues to match to any target bond.
